@startuml ControlCenter_EndToEnd_Sequence
title Meetsendai Control Center - End-to-End Tenant Lifecycle V0 (Initiator + Verifier)
skinparam maxMessageSize 150
skinparam BoxPadding 10

legend top right
  **Risk Levels (Transactions & Actor Swimlanes)**
  |<#White> Black Arrow | Internal / Low Risk Operation |
  |<#E6F2FF> Light Blue Box | Trusted Internal System Boundary |
  |<#Orange> Orange Arrow | Privileged Config / IAM (Medium Risk) |
  |<#FFE6CC> Light Orange Box| Approval Gateway (Medium Risk) |
  |<#Red> Red Arrow | Destructive / Irreversible Action (High Risk) |
  |<#FFCCCC> Light Red Box| High-Privilege Internal Admin (High Risk) |
endlegend

box "Meetsendai Internal Admins (High Privilege)" #FFCCCC
actor "CC-Initiator" as Initiator
actor "CC-Verifier" as Verifier
end box

box "Control Center Platform (Trusted Internal)" #E6F2FF
participant "Control Center\nApplication" as CC
participant "Approval &\nAudit Engine" as Audit
participant "CI/CD Pipeline" as Pipeline
participant "Terraform (IaC)" as TF
end box

box "Cloud Infrastructure (Trusted Internal)" #F2F9FF
participant "Azure Infrastructure\n& Key Vault (TDE)" as Azure
participant "Tenant SQL DB\n(Newly Provisioned)" as DB
participant "Email Service\n(Azure Communication)" as Email
end box

box "Identity & Config (Med Risk)" #FFE6CC
participant "Auth0\n(CC Admin Auth)" as EntraCC
participant "Auth0\n(Tenant Auth)" as TenantIDP
end box

box "External (Client)" #FFCCCC
actor "Tenant Primary\nContact" as PrimaryContact
end box

== 1. Control Center Login ==
Initiator -[#orange]-> EntraCC: Authenticate (MFA Required)
EntraCC --[#orange]-> Initiator: CC Session Token (CC-Initiator Role)

== 2a. Tenant Creation — Initiation ==
Initiator -[#orange]-> CC: Submit New Tenant Request\n(Name, Region, Seat Limit, Lead Threshold, Auth Type)
activate CC
CC -[#orange]-> Audit: Register Pending Request\n(Initiator locked from self-verifying)
CC -[#orange]-> Verifier: Dispatch Verification Notification
deactivate CC

== 2b. Tenant Creation — Verifier Approval ==
Verifier -[#orange]-> EntraCC: Authenticate (MFA Required)
EntraCC --[#orange]-> Verifier: CC Session Token
Verifier -[#orange]-> CC: Approve or Reject Request
activate CC
CC -[#orange]-> Audit: Log Verification Decision\n(Verifier Identity + Timestamp + Outcome)
CC -> CC: Verification passed\nInitiate Provisioning Pipeline
deactivate CC

== 2c. Automated Tenant Provisioning ==
CC -> Pipeline: Trigger Terraform Plan/Apply
activate Pipeline
Pipeline -> TF: Execute Terraform for New Tenant
activate TF
TF -[#orange]-> Azure: Provision Isolated SQL Database\n(EU Region — Azure West Europe)
TF -[#orange]-> Azure: Configure Azure Key Vault TDE\n(Tenant Database Encryption)
Azure --[#orange]-> TF: DB Provisioned & Encrypted
TF -[#orange]-> TenantIDP: Provision Auth0 Application\n(Tenant Authentication)
TenantIDP --[#orange]-> TF: Auth0 Tenant Configured
TF -[#orange]-> DB: Write Tenant Config\n(Seat Limit, Lead Threshold, EU Region Lock)
TF --> Pipeline: Provisioning Complete
deactivate TF
Pipeline -[#orange]-> Email: Dispatch Welcome Email\n(Primary Contact Address)
activate Email
Email --[#orange]-> PrimaryContact: Your Meetsendai workspace is live!\nhttps://[slug].meetsendai.com\nFirst user to register = Tenant Admin\nSetup checklist included
deactivate Email
Pipeline -[#orange]-> Audit: Write Provisioning Receipt to Audit Log
Pipeline --> Initiator: Tenant Live Notification
deactivate Pipeline

== 3. Tenant Limit Modification (Single Admin) ==
Initiator -[#orange]-> CC: Update Seat Limit or Lead Threshold
CC -[#orange]-> DB: Apply Updated Config
CC -[#orange]-> Audit: Log Limit Change\n(Initiator, Timestamp, Old/New Values)

== 4. Tenant Deletion — Initiation ==
Initiator -[#red]-> CC: Submit Tenant Deletion Request\n(Reason + Client Notification Confirmed)
activate CC
CC -[#red]-> Audit: Register Pending Deletion Request
CC -[#red]-> Verifier: Broadcast Elevated Deletion Alert
deactivate CC

== 5. Tenant Deletion — Verifier Approval ==
Verifier -[#red]-> CC: Approve Deletion
activate CC
CC -[#red]-> Audit: Log Deletion Verification\n(Verifier Identity + Timestamp)
CC -> CC: Verification passed — Begin Deletion Sequence
deactivate CC

== 6. Tenant Deletion — Execution ==
CC -[#red]-> TenantIDP: Immediately Suspend Tenant Login
CC -[#red]-> DB: Freeze Tenant Data\n(30-Day Soft-Delete Period Begins)
CC -[#orange]-> Audit: Log Suspension Timestamp

note over CC, DB
  Standard path: 30-day soft-delete retention
  (data frozen, inaccessible but retained for compliance).
  Emergency hard-delete: both Initiator AND Verifier
  must confirm in writing before pipeline executes.
end note

CC -[#red]-> Pipeline: Trigger Terraform Destroy after Retention Period
activate Pipeline
Pipeline -> TF: Terraform Destroy — Tenant Scope
TF -[#red]-> DB: Purge Tenant SQL Database
TF -[#red]-> Azure: Invalidate Azure Key Vault TDE Key
TF -[#red]-> TenantIDP: Deprovision Auth0 Tenant Application
TF --> Pipeline: Destruction Complete
deactivate Pipeline
Pipeline -[#red]-> Audit: Write Signed Deletion Receipt\nto Immutable Audit Log
Pipeline --> Initiator: Tenant Deletion Confirmed

@enduml
